      "acceptanceCriteria": "Commercial CFD solver with documented verification and validation history; version control and audit trail maintained for all simulation inputs and outputs.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022 R2 was used with documented QA procedures including version-controlled input files, solver settings logs, and output archiving. The commercial solver has an established V&V history for cardiovascular CFD applications."
