      "rationale": "Three systematically refined meshes (2.1M, 5.8M, 14.2M elements) were used to compute GCI per Roache (1998). Maximum GCI on RH index across all five operating points was 1.8%, well within the 5% acceptance criterion. Richardson extrapolation confirmed monotonic convergence."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
