      "rationale": "FDA benchmark experimental data (Hariharan et al. 2011) documents five operating points with flow rates 2.5–7 L/min and rotational speeds 2000–3500 RPM. Fluid properties (blood analogue viscosity 0.0035 Pa·s, density 1056 kg/m³) are matched to within measurement uncertainty reported in the benchmark dataset."
