      "rationale": "Simulated RH index values compared against experimental hemolysis measurements at all five FDA benchmark operating points. Maximum deviation was 14.3% at the 3500 RPM / 2.5 L/min condition; all other points within 10%. The acceptance criterion of ±20% is met at all operating points."
    },
    {
