      "rationale": "Validation was performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry under CPB-representative operating conditions. Fluid properties match clinical blood analogues. The primary difference from the COU is use of a generic rather than device-specific geometry; sensitivity analysis confirmed that hemolysis prediction trends are geometry-insensitive at MRL 2."
