      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence model selection (SST k-omega) is justified by literature precedent for rotating cardiovascular CFD; no formal model form uncertainty quantification required at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model was selected based on established precedent in cardiovascular pump CFD literature (Bludszuweit 1995, Garon & Farinas 2004). Formal model form uncertainty quantification is not required at MRL 2. Literature evidence supports adequacy of SST k-omega for predicting hemolysis-relevant shear stress distributions in centrifugal pumps."
    },
    {
