    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors met or exceeded their required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 4. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support the COU decision: identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The RH index acceptance criterion (RH < 1 relative to predicate) is supported by validated model predictions within ±20% of experimental benchmark data. The credibility assessment is accepted.",
